{"tid":2240642,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"深入淺出–攝取食用纖維的重要性","createTime":"2020-10-12T22:26:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-14T05:32:33.000Z","uid":38861,"like":74,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"e4b2cffad3c35849689bf47da5c7e28d685e7e33","tid":2240642,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T22:26:10.000Z","msg":"各款蔬果殼物均含有不同份量及款式的食用纖維，25-30克的食用纖維為每日建議的攝取量。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QvViDCk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQvViDCk.jpg&h=f0bb4ece&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n部份的食用纖維無法被腸道吸收，因而有助刺激腸道增加蠕動，防止便祕。同時它們亦有助增加飽肚感，減少進食量。<br />\n<br />\n但除此之外，攝取食用纖維還有甚麼好處呢?<br />\n<br />\n（圖2）講述之前，我們要提及一下關於膽汁的背景資料。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jcP7wXo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjcP7wXo.jpg&h=51939cf1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我們的肝臟會產生初級膽汁酸，作用是輔助脂肪在腸道裡更易被消化。<br />\n<br />\n而當初級膽汁酸抵達腸道後，聚居在腸道的細菌會將初級膽汁酸改變成為次級膽汁酸。<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）然而，某部份的次級膽汁酸對人體有害，被證實會促進腸道癌的誕生(Ref1)。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8ZjWqhr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8ZjWqhr.jpg&h=7d41a834&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而食用纖維則能夠與有害的次級膽汁酸結合，將它們帶走體外，防止它們長期聚居在腸道位置。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(圖4）另外，有部份腸道細菌依靠消化食用纖維維生。而長期沒有進食纖維的話，會導致腸道細菌品種失衡。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x13cH39.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx13cH39.jpg&h=fcb5cad9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n久而久之，進食腸道黏液的細菌品種會助大起來，它們會導致腸道壁膜更為薄弱，使腸道更容易受到感染(Ref1)。<br />\n<br />\n換句話說，攝取食用纖維能有助防止便祕、增加胞肚感以及減低腸道癌症及炎症發生的機會，絕對是不可或缺的營養。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去<span class=\"blue\">Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單</span>俾一個<span class=\"green\">like</span>以及<span class=\"red\">Bookmark</span>，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=W9k3bdIekjUozLnTtmc2V9OJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=c3d8e3c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「<span class=\"gold\">買一嚿/半嚿薯仔</span>」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=W9k3bdIekjUozLnTtmc2V9OJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=87dca2ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有興趣接收科學資訊的話，歡迎follow IG: potatopigtongue。<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S193131281830266X\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fpii%2FS193131281830266X&d=W9k3bdIekjUozLnTtmc2V9OJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=e7ace2b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S193131281830266X</a>"},{"pid":"197767370477d19ec50ff46842236be05f124706","tid":2240642,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T22:27:49.000Z","msg":"原來大腸癌係咁嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"741641aff0db0fe4e3a3dab3b0610806f970e395","tid":2240642,"uid":38861,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"197767370477d19ec50ff46842236be05f124706","tid":2240642,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1