/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾乎唔食菜但會食水果同食纖維丸仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日日有屎啊,形狀一流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8cdd8d092bc40a0b538aa720171a9c63acba3f1","tid":2240642,"uid":367564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T05:55:57.000Z","msg":"對濕疹免疫系統炎症有冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6a1d5e9016f80b28efc8bdc6c6731531fa2de30","tid":2240642,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82dfd89868d06260cf4aa6d25707ddddb9edd9a0","tid":2240642,"uid":73855,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"3d922bac14697751d6f9b36032f9abeb1a4a083a","tid":2240642,"uid":38861,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"544a07df50534c9897f257f46126f195af6b5af4","tid":2240642,"uid":73855,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T22:36:22.000Z","msg":"好似愈嚟愈易明 係咪特登寫畀我哩啲蠢人睇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T22:39:37.000Z","msg":"之前嗰幾篇寫得深入啲好似無咩迴響<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T22:44:47.000Z","msg":"大佬 你博士嚟㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁深入未必個個有興趣 仲有一見到太多學名就唔太想睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T08:59:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VtToTf4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVtToTf4.jpg&h=926aa2f7&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}